snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

snippet.title: DHURANDHAR Trailer Reaction! | Ranveer Singh | Sanjay Dutt | Akshaye Khanna
snippet.description:
Achara, Brandon and Vivan dive into the explosive trailer of Dhurander, a powerhouse Pan-India action spectacle set to redefine mass cinema! Directed with fierce vision and packed with electrifying screen presence, Dhurander brings together an unstoppable blend of high-octane action, gripping drama, and larger-than-life storytelling.

Set against the backdrop of political power, legacy, and rebellion, Dhurander follows a fearless hero rising against corruption, injustice, and a system designed to break him. With thunderous dialogue, intense character moments, and jaw-dropping set pieces, this trailer delivers every bit of the adrenaline fans were waiting for.

snippet.title: Mehrama - (Extended) Audio Lyrical | Love Aaj Kal | Kartik | Sara | Pritam | Darshan Raval | Antara
snippet.description:
Feel the soft and emotional vibe of Mehrama. Sung by Darshan Raval and Antara Mitra, this song gently reminds us of love and memories.

#mehrama #loveaajkal #darshanraval #antaramitra #pritam #kartikaaryan #saraalikhan #romantichindisongs #bollywoodsongs #hindisong #romanticsong #irshadkamil 

Credits:
Song: Mehrama Extended
Movie - Love Aaj Kal
Song - Mehrama 
Music - Pritam
Singers - Darshan Raval & Antara Mitra
Lyrics - Irshad Kamil

Lyrics:
Chahiye kisi saaye mein jagah
Chaaha bahut baar hai
Na kahin kabhi mera dil laga
Kaisa samajhdaar hai

Main na ponhchoon kyu wahan pe
Jaana chaahoon main jahaan
Main kahaan kho gaya
Aisa kya ho gaya

Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Na khabar apni rahi
Na khabar apni rahi
Na raha tera pata

Oh meharma kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Jo shor ka hissa hui
Woh aawaz hoon
Logon mein hoon
Par tanha hoon main
Haan tanha hoon main

Duniya mujhe mujhse juda hi karti rahe
Bolun magar na baatein karun
Yeh kya hoon main

Sab hai lekin main nahin hoon
Woh jo thoda tha sahi
Woh hawaa ho gaya
Kyu khafa ho gaya

Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Yun to yeh jahan paa liya
Maine hi mujhe paaya na
Hoke auron saa jaane kyun
Jeena hi mujhe aaya na

Duniya main itna uljha
Khud se main toota hoon
Mujhse hamesha main hi peeche chhoota

Main kahan kho gaya
Aisa kya ho gaya

Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Na khabar apni rahi
Na khabar apni rahi
Na raha tera pata
Oh meherma kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

snippet.title: YUNG 22 - NAPAUNE MAYA (OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO)
snippet.description:
This is my first debut album titled 22.
"22" is a musical journey through the highs and lows of love, loss, and the resilience of the human spirit. Dedicated to all those who have ever experienced heartbreak, this album weaves together raw emotions, poignant melodies, and introspective lyrics to create a cathartic listening experience.
Hope you all enjoy this albumâ¤ï¸ğŸ™

Download and stream 
https://songwhip.com/yung22

NEPAL HIPHOP RECORDS PRESENTS

PERFORMED BY - YUNG 22 AND ISHA LAMA
PROD./MIX/MAST - YUNG 22
ALLBUM COVER ART - SAMEER BASNET

VIDEO DIR. BY- FUMU
EDIT/COLOR - LUFFY AND FUMU
DRONE - HUKKE BOSS

SPECIAL THANKS TO -
ST MAN
BIG NORZZA
HUKKE SAMDI
BIG MAN
SURESH MOKTAN
AJAY TAMANG

Catch me on multiple sites
https://linktr.ee/yung_22

Connect with Yung 22 
https://www.facebook.com/YungThe22/

Connect with Yung 22
https://instagram.com/yung_22_god?igs...

Lyrics-

Timilai samjhidai basirachha yo mann aajavholi
Aankha ka saamu timra swarup darsauxa jhal jhali.

Mutu kata kata khayi rahechha
Sadhai ko lagi paraye vhaye ma
Timra ti smaran ma vhuli rahe chha.
Napaune maya ko aasha garera.

Kaile runchhuu tolauchhu harai sake ma
Dekhawati sansar ma darai rahe ma 
Maya dinchhu vhanne lai nai paraye vhaye ma
Malai kina marxau aalo ghau chalayi rahera
(Napauune maya ko aasha garera
Lai bari lai maya gayo marera)2..


Timra yaad haru bandaixan badha
Bhulna kosis garda jhan vhayidinxa gada

Bhamara hainau fula ni rahenau
Bijhxau tai ni mannma sayed holau timi kada

Mutu ka chot haru chhan ajjhai aalo
Bichhodle nisasiyera bho malai garo
Bekhabar vha raichhu ti sadyantra ra chal ko
Jiwan thakkar khayirahane samundra ko chhal vho.
